description	"Jedi Demolitionist:
A Jedi armed with a Missile Launcher, Cryo & Frag Grenades and a Lightsaber.

^2Weaponry:
- Lightsaber
-- Yellow Style Only
-- Saber Defense 0
-- 20% Less DMG
- PLX-2M Missile Launcher (4 Rockets)
- 2 Cryo Grenades
- 1 Frag Grenade

^5Force Powers:
- Jump  (2)
- Push  (1)
- Pull  (1)
- Sense (3)
- Absorb (1)

^8Attributes:
- BP Free Jumps
